            <thetext>qooxdoo-contrib is an important part of the qooxdoo ecosystem. Users of qooxdoo should be able to search, inspect and include contributions from qooxdoo-contrib.

I therefore suggest that we add a &quot;qooxdoo-contrib&quot; section in our user manual. The section could just be an introduction to the project, its scope, where to find it, what to expect from it, the tools available for it (Contrib Demobrowser), and how to integrate a contribution in one&#39;s own qooxdoo application, touching on configuration and runtime (download!) issues.

This would also raise the visibility of the qooxdoo-contrib project.</thetext>
